{"tid":1392510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致 所有「警員」們","createTime":"2019-07-31T18:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T19:20:00.000Z","uid":250369,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"678771b71ab588d0994d4c6817b7000825335f0e","tid":1392510,"uid":250369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:34:27.000Z","msg":"致 任職「警員」們<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391682</a><br />\n<br />\n等我同你講啦<br />\n而家極深藍都怕因為局勢影響經濟<br />\n搞到好多生意都唔敢接手<br />\n你地再唔保香港<br />\n市民只會越戰越勇<br />\n即使中國軍隊入城<br />\n你地要面對嘅同樣係極差嘅經濟環境<br />\n同埋能否保住飯碗嘅問題<br />\n由此可見<br />\n<br />\n請用<br />\n良知同理性分析下當下局勢<br />\n必須要做嘅事<br />\n<br />\n簡單單俾幾個問題你地<br />\n「問一問自己先」<br />\n<br />\n第一點：警員受制於邊個？<br />\n第二點：香港政府受制如邊個？<br />\n第三點：當你地做唔到野 你覺得仲有無利用價值？<br />\n第四點：當香港同中國一樣 香港係國際市場仲可以佔乜野位置？<br />\n第五點：口口聲聲話想維護「法治」 乜你覺得香港變成中國會有所謂嘅法治咩？<br />\n<br />\n請你地諗下以上5點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"0cbbfaf9b787350c2ba10aabdaf7fecb675f1a79","tid":1392510,"uid":250369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:41:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3849dc548f0d417fc837e9d284c8ff2e970d3d34","tid":1392510,"uid":250369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:41:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"090b453856e321033b0e7a87acbfd076bf35a7c4","tid":1392510,"uid":250369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:41:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"78e836e8fe60c7f26785217f7d6d4784a5663dab","tid":1392510,"uid":250369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:42:04.000Z","msg":"<span